I JUST printed this for my FF Creator Pro and installed it without a hitch.. Actually no screws either... Its tight enough fit to go on without screws so I can more easily remove it.<br />
First PLA part I tested printed very well and cooled easily.  The way the vents wrap around the back side give it good coverage from almost all angles.<br />
Couldnt be happier with this shroud. WELL DONE&gt;
